---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us | Free Estate Planning Consultation | Mesa Estate Planning"
  description="Book a free 30-minute estate planning consultation with Mesa Estate Planning. Located at 48 N Macdonald, Mesa, AZ 85201. Call (480) 000-0000 or submit our contact form."
  keywords="mesa estate planning consultation, free estate planning consultation mesa az, estate planning attorney mesa"
>
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="service-hero-content">
      <div class="service-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="bc-sep">/</span>
        <span class="bc-current">Contact</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="hero-h1" style="opacity:1;animation:none;">Let's talk about <em>your plan</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-body" style="opacity:1;animation:none;">Your first consultation is completely free. We'll learn about your situation and tell you exactly what you need — no pressure, no sales pitch.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="contact-layout">
      <div>
        <div class="contact-details">
          <div class="contact-detail"><div class="contact-icon">&#128205;</div><div><strong>Office</strong><span>48 N Macdonald, Mesa, AZ 85201</span></div></div>
          <div class="contact-detail"><div class="contact-icon">&#128222;</div><div><strong>Phone</strong><span><a href="tel:4800000000">(480) 000-0000</a></span></div></div>
          <div class="contact-detail"><div class="contact-icon">&#9993;&#65039;</div><div><strong>Email</strong><span><a href="mailto:info@mesaestateplan.com">info@mesaestateplan.com</a></span></div></div>
          <div class="contact-detail"><div class="contact-icon">&#128336;</div><div><strong>Hours</strong><span>Mon–Fri, 8am–5pm &middot; Virtual available</span></div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section" style="margin-top:40px;">
          <h2>What to Expect</h2>
          <p>The consultation takes about 30 minutes. We'll ask about your family, your assets, and what's prompting you to look at estate planning now. By the end, you'll know whether you need a trust or a will, what other documents belong in your plan, and roughly what the work involves.</p>
          <p>There's no obligation to proceed, and we'll never pressure you. If we're not the right fit, we'll tell you.</p>
          <p>Want to learn more about how we work before scheduling? Read about <a href="/our-process">our process</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-form-wrap">
        <h3>Book a Free Consultation</h3>
        <p>Tell us a bit about yourself and we'll be in touch within one business day.</p>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group"><label>First Name</label><input type="text" placeholder="McKay"></div>
          <div class="form-group"><label>Last Name</label><input type="text" placeholder="Tucker"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group"><label>Email</label><input type="email" placeholder="you@email.com"></div>
          <div class="form-group"><label>Phone</label><input type="tel" placeholder="(480) 000-0000"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>I am a...</label><select><option value="">Select...</option><option>Individual / Family</option><option>Business Owner</option><option>Financial Planner / RIA</option><option>CPA / Tax Professional</option><option>Insurance Agent</option><option>Attorney (referral)</option></select></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Service Interested In</label><select><option value="">Select a service...</option><option>Wills &amp; Trusts</option><option>Powers of Attorney</option><option>Business Succession Planning</option><option>Asset Protection</option><option>Estate Tax Planning</option><option>Not sure yet — I need guidance</option></select></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Tell us about your situation (optional)</label><textarea placeholder="e.g. Married with two kids, own a home and small business, need a trust..."></textarea></div>
        <button class="form-submit">Request Free Consultation</button>
        <p class="form-disclaimer">By submitting this form, you are not creating an attorney-client relationship. All consultations are confidential.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
